.section-grouping
  %h2(id="developer") Developer and technical communication

  %h3 Mailing lists

  %p
    Communication between Aeolus developers generally takes place using one of
    the two project mailing lists, and IRC (for real-time communication).

  %p
    %a{ :href => "https://fedorahosted.org/mailman/listinfo/aeolus-devel" } aeolus-devel
    (<a href="https://fedorahosted.org/pipermail/aeolus-devel/">archives here</a>)
    %br
    The main mailing list, used for everything except Image Warehouse.
    %br
    This mailing list has a moderate volume of traffic, and includes both
    patches proposed for inclusion, and general discussion.

  %p
    %a{ :href => "https://fedorahosted.org/mailman/listinfo/iwhd-devel" } iwhd-devel
    (<a href="https://fedorahosted.org/pipermail/iwhd-devel/">archives here</a>)
    %br
    This is a mailing list specifically for Image Warehouse development, and has
    a low to moderate amount of traffic.

  %p
    %b WARNING -
    All communication sent to these mailing lists is both public and archived,
    so don't use them for anything confidential.  For confidential matters,
    use the web form or direct email at the top of this page.

%br

