  %h2(id="security") Security related

  %p
    If you'd like to report or discuss a security vulnerability in Aeolus, please
    email aeolus-security AT fedorahosted DOT org.  Emails to this address are
    forwarded directly to senior project members, with the contents considered
    confidential (non-public) unless specifically mentioned.

  %p
    For additional security, you can optionally use GPG encryption for emails
    to this address.  The public key is available
    <a href="keys/aeolus-security-public-gpg-key.asc" title="Aeolus-security public GPG key">here</a>.

  %p
    Someone
    %b WILL
    get back to you, though it could be 24 - 48 hours (that's unusual).